<li>Brechner, K.C. (2003) Superimposed schedules applied to rent control. <i>Economic and Game Theory</i>, 2/28/03, <a href="http://www.dklevine.com/bin/workshops-php/discuss/discuss.php3?showID=396467000000000285" class="external free" title="http://www.dklevine.com/bin/workshops-php/discuss/discuss.php3?showID=396467000000000285" rel="nofollow">http://www.dklevine.com/bin/workshops-php/discuss/discuss.php3?showID=396467000000000285</a>.</li>
